Class Booster

  • java.lang.Object
    • Obstacle
      • Booster

  • public class Booster
extends Obstacle
    The Booster class is represented by a slightly transparent green rectangle, which accelerates the Player in the direction that it is moving. This class intentionally doesn't have a hitbox, as the interaction with the Player is calculated in its act method. This class extends Obstacle. Basis copied from Wall class, created by Jensen.
    Author:
    Edward
